21 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 26, Chapter 52, Subchapter 4, is
22 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
23 26-52-457. Parts for and repair of agricultural equipment and
24 machinery — Definitions.
25 (a) As used in this section:
26 (1)(A) "Agricultural equipment and machinery" means implements
27 used exclusively and directly in farming.
28 (B) “Agricultural equipment and machinery” includes
29 without limitation:
30 (i) Irrigation pipe used to carry water from an
31 irrigation well to the crops produced in farming regardless of whether the
32 irrigation pipe is used above ground or is buried underground;
33 (ii) Aviation machinery and equipment; and
34 (iii) Implements used to harvest crops produced in
35 farming by others.
36 (C) “Agricultural equipment and machinery” does not
